                Hablemos
            </a>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="process-section">
        <h3>¿Cómo trabajamos?</h3>
        <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
                <span class="step-number">1</span>
                <h4>Discovery</h4>
                <p>Hablamos de tus objetivos y definimos qué necesitas realmente.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <span class="step-number">2</span>
                <h4>Desarrollo</h4>
                <p>Diseño y programo tu web manteniéndote informado del avance.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <span class="step-number">3</span>
                <h4>Lanzamiento</h4>
                <p>Publicamos tu web y te enseño a usarla para que tengas el control.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .services-container {
        padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    .services-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .services-header h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: var(--text-main);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .services-header p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .highlight {
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* GRID DE PRECIOS */
    .pricing-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    /* TARJETA DE PRECIO */
    .pricing-card {
        background: var(--surface); /* Fondo dinámico */
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        position: relative;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .pricing-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        border-color: var(--accent); /* Borde azul al pasar el mouse */
    }

    /* TARJETA POPULAR */
    .pricing-card.popular {
        border: 2px solid var(--accent);
        background: var(--surface);
        transform: scale(1.05); /* Un poco más grande siempre */
        z-index: 10;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px -10px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15); /* Sombra azulada suave */
    }

    .pricing-card.popular:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-5px);
    }

    .badge-popular {
        position: absolute;
        top: -15px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        background: var(--accent);
        color: white;
        padding: 6px 16px;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    /* TEXTOS INTERNOS */
    .card-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .card-header h3 {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--text-main);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
    }

    .subtitle {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }

    .price {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--text-main);
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    /* LISTA DE CARACTERÍSTICAS */
    .features {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
        flex-grow: 1; 
    }

    .features li {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--text-main); /* Texto legible */
        font-size: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    /* BOTONES */
    .cta-button {
        display: block;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-button.primary {
        background: var(--accent);
        color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px var(--accent-glow);
    }

    .cta-button.primary:hover {
        background: var(--accent-dark);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    
    .cta-button.outline {
        border: 2px solid var(--border);
        color: var(--text-main);
        background: transparent;
    }

    .cta-button.outline:hover {
        border-color: var(--accent);
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* PROCESO */
    .process-section {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 3rem;
        background: var(--surface);
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    
    .process-section h3 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: var(--text-main);
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .steps {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 3rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .step {
        flex: 1;
        min-width: 250px;
    }

    .step-number {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        background: var(--accent);
        color: white;
        border-radius: 50%;
        line-height: 50px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px var(--accent-glow);
    }

    .step h4 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        color: var(--text-main);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .step p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .pricing-card.popular {
            transform: scale(1); /* Quitamos el zoom en móvil para que no se salga */
        }
        .services-header h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
        .steps {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>